# The New School IRL Web App - Additional Pages

We will update the application structure to reflect the new designs provided, incorporating the tabbar navigation and adding the new requested pages for "FIND CLUB" and "BROWSE CLASSES".

## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] index.html & styles.css
- **Quick Links UI Update**: Transform the vertical "Quick Links" buttons into a clean, horizontal tab bar (FIND CLUB | BROWSE CLASSES | CREATE EVENTS) with an active state underline (red), matching `iPhone 16 Plus - 8`.
- Apply micro-interactions to these tabs.

### [NEW] find_club.html
When a user taps the "FIND CLUB" tab, they will navigate to this new page, which is focused on upcoming events and calendars (matching the CALENDAR screen wireframes `18`/`19`/`20`).
- **Header**: "CALENDAR" text.
- **Content**: 
  - `Upcoming Sessions` list (events like "Design wireframes", "Eat donuts").
  - `Your Events` calendar section (showing a monthly date picker with active red dates).
  - Add "+ Add new" small red action links above lists.

### [NEW] browse_classes.html
When a user taps the "BROWSE CLASSES" tab, they will navigate to this page, focusing on class details and activities (matching the `LCOD-3010` screen wireframe `14`).
- **Header**: "LCOD-3010" text (in red).
- **Content**:
  - `Upcoming Sessions` list for the class.
  - `Your Classes Activities` mini-calendar/timeline.
  - `Last Messages in Chat Room` list item showing recent chats.

### [MODIFY] app.js
- Include logic across pages for the bottom navigation bar active states depending on the URL.
- Basic navigation hooks for the new Quick Link horizontal tabs.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Navigate between [index.html](file:///Users/ijuyeon/Desktop/tns_irl_draft2/index.html), `find_club.html`, and `browse_classes.html` by clicking the Quick Link tabs.
2. Confirm that the UI of the Quick Links is horizontal and clearly indicates an active state on each associated page.
3. Validate that the new list formats (Upcoming Sessions, Chat Messages) and the custom calendar view appear visually polished.
